"{\"uid\": \"thepinknews.com-2024-08-06-drag-race-star-nicky-doll-sues-laurence-fox-after-olympic-opening-ceremony-pedos-post\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"French Drag Race star Nicky Doll is going ahead with suing Laurence Fox after he referred to her and other drag queens as 'deviant little pedos'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999955880804928, \"rank\": 4.3442231923380095e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicky Doll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\"}, {\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurence Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Leon Neal/Getty Images/X)  French Drag Race star Nicky Doll is going ahead with suing Laurence Fox after he referred to her and other drag queens as 'deviant little pedos'.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicky Doll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\"}, {\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurence Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Leon Neal/Getty Images/X)  RuPaul's Drag Racestar Nicky Doll has followed through on her threat to sue Laurence Fox over a social media post shared during the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicky Doll\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicky_Doll\"}, {\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurence Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday (2 August), Doll announced in a post on X/Twitter post she is launching legal action against the formerLewisstar who called participants in the opening extravaganza\\\"deviant little pedos\\\".\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The French drag queen shared a letter which confirmed she will be going ahead with a defamation complaint against former GB News presenter Fox and others.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999955880804928, \"rank\": 4.3442231923380095e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GB News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\"}, {\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9997744307293991, \"rank\": 0.00013313840020494217, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She captioned a letter, which was also posted on X by her lawyer,Anne-Sophie Laguens: \\\"I will never again allow myself and other queer people to be defamed and demonised.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If responding with love does not work for some, then responding with justice should work.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See you in court.\\\"\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter reads: \\\"Following the opening ceremony of the Olympic Games on July 26, the artists who performed on the Debilly footbridge suffered an unprecedented wave of hatred and faced the trivialisation of insults due to their sexual orientation or gender identity.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passerelle_Debilly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Debilly footbridge\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passerelle_Debilly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Passerelle_Debilly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The lawyers ofStop Homophobiehave received numerous reports of incitement to hatred, insults, online harassment, threats and defamation.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The firm was notified by Mr Karl Sanchez, known as Nicky Doll, of a defamation complaint filed against Mr Laurence Fox and other users of the social network X (Twitter).\\\"\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1677, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurence Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurence_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Merci de d\\u00e9fendre les artistes queers contre la haine.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nous sommes avec vous.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It added that her participation in the \\\"festivity\\\" segment of the opening ceremony led her to suffer \\\"an unprecedented wave of animosity\\\" and even death threats.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter notes that messages sent to her \\\"convey hateful and defamatory conflations, equating drag performances and pedophilia\\\".\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox wassuccessfully sued for libelearlier this year byRuPaul's Drag Racestar Crystal and former Stonewall trustee Simon Blake, following a separate exchange on X.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9997744307293991, \"rank\": 0.00013313840020494217, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4359631301895335e-29, \"text\": \"Stonewall\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stonewall_riots\"}, {\"begin\": 2236, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"score\": 0.6977504022888985, \"rank\": 0.4331772129699256, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blake_Carrington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The LGBTQ+ stories you do not want to miss, delivered to your inbox daily.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for registering!\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can update your email subscriptions at any time in theMy profilesection of your account.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related articles  Latest News    What to buy now    Exclusive    Download the PinkNews app  Award winning LGBTQ+ journalism  About us  Editorial Policy  Contact us  Advertise  Work for us    Terms and conditions  Privacy policy\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": []}]}"